[resource]
script = ExtResource( 1 )
syntax_version = 2
raw_text = "~ first_visit

Upon entering the room,a sudden bolt of lightning struck. A blink later, a short figure in lab coat with long dark hair and oval glasses appeared.
{{YELLOW_TEACHER}}: Students! So sorry for startling you. I am preparing a demonstration for next class.
if blue_joined == true
	{{GREEN}}: I'm fine, do not worry about it! I am just here to show {{BLUE}} around the {{YELLOW_ASPECT}} students' classroom.
else
	{{GREEN}}: I'm fine, do not worry about it! I am just looking around.
{{YELLOW_TEACHER}}: Feel free to look around. Just make sure to read the safety signs and avoid touching anything!
The room has several stations with various electrostatic machines and mounting boards. {{GREEN}} goes to one of these stations.
if blue_joined == true
	{{GREEN}}: In this room, the {{YELLOW_ASPECT}} students learn how to control electrical and light phenomena. They also learn how to move very quickly, which is somehow related to this.
	{{BLUE}} nods.
- Leave => yellow_corridor_end

~ visit

{{GREEN}} visits the {{YELLOW_ASPECT}} aspect's classroom.
- Leave => yellow_corridor_end

~ execute_action

No problems here.
set next = \"yellow_classroom\"

~ yellow_corridor_end

{{GREEN}} leaves the classroom.
set next = \"yellow_corridor_end\""
